ties\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to them, we live in a \\\"patriarchy\\\" where men are free to wear and show whatever they want while women are oppressed and their bodies are censored because they are \\\"objectified\\\".\", \"from\": 11841, \"to\": 12028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, this shows the contrary: men are the ones who can not even give the impression they are revealing more than they \\\"should\\\".\", \"from\": 12029, \"to\": 12160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And while a lot of people (especially, women and queer men) opt to hypersexualize and objectify, others claim for censorship because it's \\\"inappropriate\\\" that men show that much of skin.\", \"from\": 12161, \"to\": 12347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jesus Christ what is this, a who-has-it-worse competition?\", \"from\": 12349, \"to\": 12407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fact is that practically all major roles in the world (including those responsible for athlete dresscodes) are occupied by men so feel free to complain there if you disagree with something.\", \"from\": 12408, \"to\": 12601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A perfect example of a double standard is that women can be arrested for walking around topless since that counts as \\\"indecent exposure\\\" while it's perfectly acceptable for men to walk around without a shirt.\", \"from\": 12602, \"to\": 12810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"dump woke  This comment is hidden.Click here to view.\", \"from\": 12812, \"to\": 12865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Exactly who do you think \\\"forces\\\" women to wear the teeny tiny bikini bottoms when playing beach volleyball?\", \"from\": 12867, \"to\": 12975, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never heard a single complaint by the female players or by the audience, so this is a win-win.\", \"from\": 12976, \"to\": 13077, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The tiny bikinis have not only improved the capabilities of t